---
/**
 * rest-api · 0011 · Figure 2 — "The interviewer's rubric" scorecard
 * (junior vs senior across structure, breadth, judgment).
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from
 * docs/rest-api/lessons/0011-mock-interview-whiteboard-design.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an .astro component for the same reason
 * as Fig1: raw inline SVG with kebab-case attributes is unreliable inside MDX,
 * but is plain HTML inside .astro.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 200"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A scorecard contrasting a junior answer with a senior answer across structure, breadth, and judgment"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="320"
                y="16"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">THE INTERVIEWER'S RUBRIC</text
            >
            <!-- column headers -->
            <text x="120" y="42" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700">SIGNAL</text>
            <rect x="220" y="28" width="190" height="22" rx="6" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="315"
                y="43"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">JUNIOR</text
            >
            <rect x="424" y="28" width="208" height="22" rx="6" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="528"
                y="43"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">SENIOR</text
            >

            <!-- row 1 -->
            <text
                x="120"
                y="76"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Structure</text
            >
            <text x="120" y="89" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >did you clarify first?</text
            >
            <rect x="220" y="62" width="190" height="36" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text x="315" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >jumps to endpoints</text
            >
            <rect x="424" y="62" width="208" height="36" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text x="528" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >5 min of requirements first</text
            >

            <!-- row 2 -->
            <text
                x="120"
                y="124"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Breadth</text
            >
            <text x="120" y="137" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >covered 5 dimensions?</text
            >
            <rect x="220" y="110" width="190" height="36" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect>
            <text x="315" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >CRUD only, no auth/async</text
            >
            <rect x="424" y="110" width="208" height="36" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect>
            <text x="528" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >idempotency, paging, BOLA, async</text
            >

            <!-- row 3 -->
            <text
                x="120"
                y="172"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Judgment</text
            >
            <text x="120" y="185" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >named a trade-off?</text
            >
            <rect x="220" y="158" width="190" height="36" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect>
            <text x="315" y="180" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >"it'll just scale"</text
            >
            <rect x="424" y="158" width="208" height="36" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect>
            <text x="528" y="180" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >says what changes at 100×</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        A senior who walks a clear checklist and narrates the <em>why</em> beats one who free-associates
        brilliant fragments.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
